  <scopecontent id="aspace_6e4797a07ddb4dc772fbb7f39bc38a09">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Annotated student scrapbooks, compiled by students in Professor Carol Kammen's History 126 course for Spring 2007, documenting the Cornell experience especially the freshman experience. Compilers include Ariana Almeida, Leslie Chae, Peter Franz, Lisa Han, Nicole Handy, Emma Herzog, Edward Kim, Jr., Jen Koh, Samantha Krotz, Sora Lee, Scott Marrett, Natalie McClain, Kaitlyn McKeown, Ryan McNamara, Kate Morris, Alyssa Padover, Leif Paulson, and Liz Peters.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <userestrict id="aspace_6b82a24b2f1e30609b3a18f394fb18a9">
